WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
What did you find to do at night then?

00:00:02.880 --> 00:00:08.400
Well, well we did, shouldn't have do much as I said, we would go to Bandaropan and watch them, but anyhow

00:00:09.560 --> 00:00:16.560
We'd go out some nights, me and my sister, we were supposed to be always go out, we'd meet one another,

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:18.880
we'd go out when we were kids, go out, right.

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:24.000
There used to be the swimming-mouths up there years ago and they had

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:26.960
dancing up there first.

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:33.960
And me and my sister we still love, and of course it's on our way home, like, you know, we still love,

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:40.120
oh, we wish we could go in, you know, we used to sit on the steps and watch because we knew we'd dare not go in, you see.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
And oh, we'd say, wouldn't we like to go in? And my father used to say, yes,

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:47.640
let me catch you in there.

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:52.240
I'll come, I'll strap you in front of all of them.

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:55.120
I was too scared.

00:00:55.280 --> 00:01:01.000
But we'd sit on the steps, I'd pass the door open the door, and we'd have a peep to see these youngsters

00:01:01.720 --> 00:01:03.720
dancing in there.

